page.title: 07CUB SCOUTS
page.content: All the boys from Icomb usally go to stow-on_the_World or Kingham and Churchill if they want to join Cubs. There are no cub packs in Icomb my name is Vere Oldridge i go to Kingham and Churchill pack These are some of the things we do. We go on nature walks. Some times we go camping. learning knots, playing football, crab_football, cricket and roan'ders. You leave cubs when you are 11 years old then you go on to scouts my best thing in cubs is camping. i go to cubs once a week on monday at 6.00 pm and it finishes at 7.30 pm .
